graph.description: Describes how to document the sources used in the compilation or enhancement of heritage assets. This information provides authority for the entries without which the entries have no substantiating evidence. The information also allows future users to trace the origin of a given entry and to avoid the inefficiency of re-examining sources that have already been checked.
